  "title": "Receptionist - Central Area / 5 days [SAS]",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Provide a high-touch, professional reception experience, ensuring all guests and VIPs are warmly welcomed and well supported</p></li><li><p>Coordinate VIP guest arrivals, departures, and meeting arrangements with discretion and professionalism</p></li><li><p>Oversee front desk operations, including call handling, email correspondence, and visitor management</p></li><li><p>Manage meeting room reservations and coordinate hospitality services as required</p></li><li><p>Collaborate closely with internal stakeholders to support executive and guest requirements</p></li><li><p>Maintain reception and guest areas to consistently high, premium standards<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p><p></p></li></ul>",
